# BIDS Dataset for fMRI Study

This dataset contains fMRI data for a removal task.
Data includes:
  - Anatomical T1-weighted images
  - Functional BOLD images
  - Field maps for distortion correction

Subjects: 43
Sessions: 2 per subject (except where noted)
Task: removal

